        public boolean equals(java.lang.Object o)
        This is used for merging the results coming from the three servers. The comparison is made by firstly comparing the tv rage id, imdb id and then by title. If at least one pair of values is identical, the two TvSeriesEntity objects are considered as being equal as well.
